<h2>Location</h2>

<p>The Redox Biology course is usually held on Tuesday afternoons (4:00 – 6:00 PM) on the Bethesda Campus (Bldg. 50, Rooms 1227/1233). This course is also&nbsp; videocast to NCI-Frederick (Bldg. 549, Room A).</p>

<p>The course consists of two 1-hour lectures.&nbsp; Each session will have a 50-minute lecture with ample time for discussion and analysis. A handout for each lecture will be distributed on site.</p>

