<h2>Related Training Opportunities</h2>

<p>This course is part of an ongoing training curriculum for NCI clinical and postdoctoral fellows. Each fall CCR offers the “Translational Research in Clinical Oncology (TRACO)” course, hosted by Dr. Terry Moody. Another course, "Demystifying Medicine" is held each spring. This course provides 2 hours of lecture each week (January – May) and is hosted by Dr. Irvin M. Arias. To learn about additional training opportunities at NIH, visit <a alt="https://www.training.nih.gov/" href="https://www.training.nih.gov/" target="_blank" title="https://www.training.nih.gov/">https://www.training.nih.gov/</a></p>
